<h2 id="object-expressionsê³¼-declarationsì‚¬ì´ì˜-ì˜ë¯¸ë¡ ì -ì°¨ì´">Object Expressionsê³¼ Declarationsì‚¬ì´ì˜ ì˜ë¯¸ë¡ ì  ì°¨ì´</h2>
